{"about_the_game":"Waking up from a deep sleep, you found yourself lost in another world - Diablo the Abyss! <br>This's a treacherous place, where danger lurks and monsters roam freely. <br>Determined to find a way back home, you embark on the adventure.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1945230/extras/hit.gif?t=1734093729\" /><br><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Key Features:</h2></strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Random World</strong>: Explore an eighteen-floors Great Abyss with <strong>randomly generated</strong> terrains, environments, and events. Brace yourself for entirely <strong>unknown challenges and thrilling opportunities</strong>!</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Diverse Terrains</strong>: Venture through various landscapes, from fruit-laden forests and mineral-rich rocky terrains to fish-filled yet treacherous water bodies. Unravel the mysteries of dangerous zones like deserts, swamps, and snowy regions, rarely visited by humans.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Freedom of Strategy</strong>: <strong>Plan your time freely.</strong> Are you working in the city or embarking on daring adventures? Gathering fruits for food or mining for money? Adapt your strategy to the ever-changing resources and the random world!</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Abundant Equipments</strong>: Over <strong>500 equipments</strong> with <strong>random quality</strong> and <strong>random affixes</strong>! Catering to your styles and building strategies.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Fortuitous Teammates</strong>: Over <strong>70 different characters</strong>, each with unique attributes and skills! You may fortuitously meet some of them in your journey. How will you develop them, and then form a tacit and powerful team team?</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Concise Main Plot</strong>: Seamlessly blend the richness of random gameplay with a straightforward and compelling narrative, making your gaming experience purposeful and engaging.</li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Just Like a Dream","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1945230/1ab546674bd481aa9001b3769c90abd7bb2d22d7.jpg"},{"name":"Living in the Moment","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1945230/eefe22aac95c2fc93b8e6aa6a8a35e4803364f31.jpg"},{"name":"Sweat Dream","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1945230/f55d6f49405ccd5faffb20b73b24a41256f8655f.jpg"},{"name":"A Little Challenge","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1945230/ab343ea4934b160a18e37754048bc678514915cf.jpg"},{"name":"The Deadline","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1945230/a5118b6a9e650888a64768234fc73147b438c022.jpg"},{"name":"Backpedaled","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1945230/04cc49eb182a1ee5f0d18d5510b11e8adad6f7d4.jpg"},{"name":"New Start","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1945230/fdc058ce2e6bfbcec733ee82f570d4afa5fc5e41.jpg"},{"name":"One-Xin City","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1945230/fdc058ce2e6bfbcec733ee82f570d4afa5fc5e41.jpg"},{"name":"Two-Rock City","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1945230/fdc058ce2e6bfbcec733ee82f570d4afa5fc5e41.jpg"},{"name":"Three-Hall City","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1945230/fdc058ce2e6bfbcec733ee82f570d4afa5fc5e41.jpg"}],"total":100},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1945230/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1734093729","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1945230/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1734093729","capsule_image":"https://shared.akam